 * SIGMA is a library of algorithms for highly accurate algorithms for
 * computation of SVD, PSVD, QSVD, (H,K)-SVD, and for solution of the
 * eigenvalue problems Hx = lambda M x, H M x = lambda x with H, M > 0.
